lead_paragraph: Germany midfielder Bastian Schweinsteiger is struggling to get fit for this year's European Championship, Manchester United manager Louis van Gaal said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Schweinsteiger Doubtful for Euro 2016, Says Van Gaal
